# ðŸš€ HooxIPO Deployment Guide (Vercel + GitHub)

To deploy your application, you should create **two separate** projects on Vercel from the same GitHub repository. This ensures the Frontend (Vite) and Backend (FastAPI) are handled correctly.

## 1. Prerequisites
1.  Push your entire `ipo_tracker_alert` folder to a **GitHub repository**.
2.  Log in to [Vercel](https://vercel.com).

---

## 2. Deploying the Backend
1.  Click **"Add New..."** > **Project** on your Vercel dashboard.
2.  Select the **`ipo-alert-system`** repository (âš ï¸ **IMPORTANT**: Do NOT select `stock-alert-system` as it contains old Next.js code).
3.  **Project Name**: `hoox-ipo-backend`
4.  **Root Directory**: Click "Edit" and select the `backend` folder.
5.  **Framework Preset**: Select **"Other"**.
6.  **Environment Variables**:
    *   `SUPABASE_URL`: (Copy from your backend [.env](file:///c:/Users/N.VenkataRaghuCharan/Desktop/Tharun/Projects/ipo_tracker_alert/backend/.env))
    *   `SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY`: (Copy from your backend [.env](file:///c:/Users/N.VenkataRaghuCharan/Desktop/Tharun/Projects/ipo_tracker_alert/backend/.env))
    *   `DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL`: (Optional)
7.  Click **Deploy**.
8.  **Important**: Once deployed, copy the **Deployment URL** (e.g., `https://hoox-ipo-backend.vercel.app`).

---

## 3. Deploying the Frontend
1.  Go back to your Vercel Dashboard and click **"Add New..."** > **Project**.
2.  Select the **same GitHub repository** again.
3.  **Project Name**: `hoox-ipo-frontend`
4.  **Root Directory**: Click "Edit" and select the `frontend` folder.
5.  **Framework Preset**: Select **"Vite"** (Vercel should detect this automatically).
6.  **Environment Variables**:
    *   `VITE_API_BASE_URL`: Paste the **Backend Deployment URL** you copied in Step 2.
    *   `VITE_SUPABASE_URL`: (Copy from your [frontend/.env.local](file:///c:/Users/N.VenkataRaghuCharan/Desktop/Tharun/Projects/ipo_tracker_alert/frontend/.env.local))
    *   `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`: (Copy from your [frontend/.env.local](file:///c:/Users/N.VenkataRaghuCharan/Desktop/Tharun/Projects/ipo_tracker_alert/frontend/.env.local))
7.  Click **Deploy**.

---

## 4. Final Verification
*   Open your **Frontend** URL.
*   Login/Signup to verify the connection to the Backend.
*   Check the **Profited/Losted** and **Alerts** pages to ensure data is flowing.

> [!TIP]
> Whenever you push changes to GitHub, Vercel will automatically redeploy both the Frontend and Backend for you!
